{"tid":1628373,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做黑警奶共,日後會否得到中共關照?","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:50:19.000Z","uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cea9f8adc528e8f5daba7ef34e385421b6c30427","tid":1628373,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"依家做黑警奶共,日後會否得到中共關照?<br />\n錢，女人，私樓?<br />\n<br />\n用完即棄 輸打贏要 恩將仇報係偉大祖國一大特色黎，黑警有人唔做做狗暴打市民，做過街老鼠為乜，點解唔一齊對付林鄭創造新香港?"},{"pid":"5ef3177eaeff4fca38c2aa7e9f385193924d32a3","tid":1628373,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"請支持行動post<br />\n<br />\n【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"f3fbef07210b8e767a06d43e24ba4890f76dbe61","tid":1628373,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535e25d96a2c9e3ffbaad79b76f4d1efbcc25969","tid":1628373,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https: